'''Lonatran Zoo''' was a huge biological reserve maintained by the [[Gree (species)/Legends|Gree]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lonatro]]. It covered huge portions of the planet's surface and was home to curators who watched over [[Species/Legends|species]] that were extinct on other [[Gree Enclave/Legends|Gree Enclave]] worlds and many naturally evolved species.<ref name="The Gree Enclave">{{JournalCite|8|The Gree Enclave}}</ref>

